title: [1958] Cannonball Adderley - Things Are Getting Better (320kbps)
description:
Great sounding remastered version ripped from a SACD in 320kbps. Features artists such as Wynton Kelly on piano, Percy Heath on bass, & Art Blakey on drums. Recorded at Reeves Sound Studios in New York City on October 28, 1958. 

01. Blues Oriental                      [4:59 ]
02. Things Are Getting Better           [7:10 ]
03. Serves Me Right (Take 5)            [4:45 ]
04. Serves Me Right (Take 4)            [4:35 ]
05. Groovin' High                       [5:20 ]
06. The Sidewalks of New York (Take 5)  [6:57 ]
07. The Sidewalks of New York (Take 4)  [5:12 ]
08. Sounds For Sid                      [6:24 ]
09. Just One of Those Things            [6:45 ]

Tracks 4 & 7 are bonus tracks that were not featured on the original LP.
